title: Paul Kalkbrenner performing “Te Quiero” live at Cercle Odyssey in Los Angeles.

author: Cercle
description:
Back in 2010, Stromae released "Te Quiero" a fragile yet obsessive love song. Captured live at Cercle Odyssey, Paul Kalkbrenner's remix transforms these emotional lyrics into an irresistible dance experience. His hypnotic techno beats convert sadness into pure energy on the dance floor.
